author: Jonathan Sawyer
title: Matty Matheson Links With StreetX for Amazing Capsule Collection
text:
Visit the original post to see all 14 images from this gallery. 
StreetX has joined with chef and Viceland star Matty Matheson for a special collaborative capsule. In following up on an initial release, which saw the product sell out in one day, the collection is now becoming available in a bigger way.
Featuring hoodies, graphic tees and a tote bag, the project plays on the tongue in cheek tagline seen throughout, glorifying Matty in a cheeky manner that is synonymous with both StreetX and Matty.
Youâ€™ll be able to shop the delivery online beginning Tuesday, March 21 at 10 p.m. EST.
